    <p>Visiting researchers will need access to basic research services (e.g., library, email access, labs and work space). The Ryerson faculty host/supervisor is responsible for arranging&nbsp; access for the visitor to relevant University facilities; this includes completing the <a href="https://library.ryerson.ca/services/borrower/cards/application/" target="_blank">request form for the OneCard<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a> and library access.&nbsp;</p> 
