    <p>Ryerson International/Human Resources will provide visiting researchers with a <a href="/content/dam/ri/visitors/2019-Researcher-PreArrival-Manual.pdf"><span class="sr-only">PDF file</span>Foreign Researchers Pre-Arrival Manual<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-file-pdf-o"></span></a> to assist them in making arrangements prior to their arrival in Toronto. Ryerson International will also arrange orientation sessions for international visiting research students and for international visiting scholars/professors. &nbsp;A date and time for the session will be provided upon arrival.</p>
    





