<p>When determining the start and end dates of the visit please be sure to take into consideration internal <a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-processing-times.html" target="_blank">processing times<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a> and visa/work permit processing times that range depending on the visitor's nationality and location of the visa office.</p> 
